message: “Today’s verdict should send a strong message that this Office, together with our law enforcement partners, will work tirelessly to identify those who would sexually exploit minors and prosecute those abusers to the fullest extent of the law.”

data.description: Sean Price, 39, met the Australian teen online and encouraged her to join him in New York. The superseding indictment charged him with interstate and foreign enticement to engage in sexual activity, interstate and foreign transportation of a minor to engage in sexual activity, a Mann Act violation,�...
data.title: ICE New York trafficking investigation results in criminal conviction, victim rescued
